title: Bug 121682: Exception throws when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description:
Description: Exception throws when exporting data from the attached report.
Steps to reproduce:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Export the data in the table.

Expected result: The data is exported.
Actual result: An exception is thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() function.
OB: An exception is thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() function when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map.
EB: The data in the table should be exported successfully without any exceptions.
SR:
To reproduce:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Export the data in the table.
